Change a
{jjdhr_heat_p}
status between
{jjdhe_racing}
and
{jjdhe_stabled},
or rename its
{jjdhm_silks}.

{jjds_arguments}

//axd_required
* {jjdt_firemark}
— target
{jjdhr_heat}

//axd_optional
* `--racing` — set status to
{jjdhe_racing}

//axd_optional
* `--stabled` — set status to
{jjdhe_stabled}

//axd_optional
* {jjda_silks}
— new display name

*Requirements:* At least one of `--racing`, `--stabled`, or {jjda_silks} must be provided.

{jjds_stdout} None

{jjds_exit_uniform} 0 success, non-zero error.

{jjds_behavior}

.
{jjdr_load};
on failure, exit immediately with
{jjdr_load}
error status
. Verify
{jjdhr_heat}
exists with given
{jjdt_firemark}
. Verify at least one argument provided (`--racing`, `--stabled`, or {jjda_silks})
. If status change requested:
.. Error if heat is
{jjdhe_retired}
(terminal state)
.. Update
{jjdhm_status}
to new value (same-status request is allowed; idempotent no-op)
.. Move
{jjdhr_heat}
to just before the first heat with the target status in
{jjdgm_order}
(if no heats of that status exist, append to end)
. If {jjda_silks} provided:
.. Update
{jjdhm_silks}
to new value
.
{jjdr_save}

*Validation errors:*

[cols="2,3"]
|===
| Condition | Error

| No arguments provided
| "At least one of --racing, --stabled, or --silks required"

| Heat is retired
| "Cannot furlough retired heat {firemark}"
|===

